  "title": "RPM—Ep. 42 | Private debt in the high-rate era with Richard Schmidt and Jovan Samardzic",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>StepStone Group- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2024-06-17T17:04:55+00:00\" title=\"Monday, June 17, 2024 - 17:04\">Mon, 06/17/2024 - 17:04</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">RPM—Ep. 42 | Private debt in the high-rate era with Richard Schmidt and Jovan Samardzic</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"StepStone\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-06/Featured-5_0.jpg\" height=\"381\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-06/Featured-5_0.jpg\" width=\"908\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p>In this episode of RPM, Richard Schmidt, Senior Analyst, Private Debt, and Jovan Samardzic, Managing Director, Private Debt Research, join co-host Michael Venne to discuss the state of the private debt market. They cover:</p><ul><li>The relative value of private debt (2:12);</li><li>The impact of higher interest rates (4:42);</li><li>How middle-market companies are performing (6:57);</li><li>What’s ahead for default and loss rates (8:20); and</li><li>The outlook for direct lending volumes (10:26).</li></ul><p></p><p>Read the transcript .</p><p>RPM is available on <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/rpm-reflections-on-private-markets/id1537055419\">Apple Podcasts</a> and <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/1xZBHwyP2Bx6RRkMJKXOaP\">Spotify</a>—anywhere you normally get your podcasts. Subscribe today!</p><div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items\"><div class=\"field__item\"><h3>The InsuranceAUM.com podcast is available on</h3><div class=\"btns-wrapper\"> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6WIbsYrL1BXuJMPsZXSk8R\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn2.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/insuranceaum-com/id1500643401\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn3.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/InsuranceAUM-com/dp/B08K57V1D6\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/Frame%20366%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@InsuranceAUMCommunity\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/frame_366%20%281%29%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-4-lg\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><h4>Share this post</h4> <span class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 addtoany_list d-flex gap-2 justify-content-start\" data-a2a-title=\"RPM—Ep. 42 | Private debt in the high-rate era with Richard Schmidt and Jovan Samardzic\" data-a2a-url=\"https://insuranceaum.